            <h2>Silver Airways Cancellation Policy</h2>
            <p>Silver Airways is one of the regional airlines of the United States founded in 2011. Domestically, the airline has served flights from its Fort Lauderdale, Orlando, and Tampa hubs in Florida, as well as Essential Air Services based in Atlanta (Georgia), Billings (Montana), Boston (Massachusetts), Cleveland (Ohio), and Washington D.C. </p>
            <p>The airline has also served international routes between Florida and the Bahamas, and in March 2020 began its own operations based in San Juan (Puerto Rico) to surrounding destinations in the Caribbean. </p>
            <p>Apart from easy booking, the airlines also ensure effortless <b>flight cancellation</b>. Let’s have a look at the <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/silver-airways-cancellation-policy.aspx">cancellation policy of Silver Airways </a>so that you can decide on the best airline for a comfortable travel experience. </p>
            <h2>Cancellation </h2>
            <p>You can cancel your flight reservation within 24 hours of booking the flight without paying any cancellation fee. Also, the booking must be made at least 7 days before the departure of the flight. However, if you fail to <b>cancel the ticket within 24 hours </b>you will have to pay the cancellation fee. If you are a freedom fare customer, you would have to pay 90 USD. </p>
            <p>Please keep in mind that the cancellation fee is extra for international trips as compared to domestic ones. </p>
            <h3>Refund </h3>
            <p>If you manage to cancel the flight within 24 hours, you are eligible for a 100% refund. You will receive the refund in the same way the <a href="https://www.faresmatch.com/">flight booking</a> was done. </p>
            <p>If you have made payment by cash or cheques, you can reach out to the airline and seek reimbursement in the desired manner. </p>
            <h4>frequently asked questions</h4>
            <h3>How to cancel a flight ticket with Silver Airways? </h3>
            <p>You can call the Silver airline customer care office and inform them about the cancellation. You may also contact your kiosk to help you through the cancellation process. Apart from this, you may also visit the official website of the airlines and cancel your flight ticket. </p>
            <h3>When can I make the request for the refund? By when can I expect it? </h3>
            <p>You can make a request for a refund by filling out a refund request form on Silver Airways’ official website. The refund will reflect within 7 to 20 business days from the cancellation. </p>
            <h3>Can I ask for compensation if my flight gets delayed by 2 hours? </h3>
            <p>If your replacement flight delays your arrival by 2 or more hours or your flight was canceled less than 14 days before departure, you are eligible to get compensation. </p>
            <h3>How to check if my flight is refundable? </h3>
            <p>You can check if your flight is refundable by visiting the official website of the airline and entering the ticket or document number and Silver Airways website will display refund eligibility and information. </p>
